               <p>1728. 
               
                  <persName id="t18290910-197-defend1827" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN 
                     COOK
                  <interp inst="t18290910-197-defend1827" type="surname" value="COOK"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290910-197-defend1827" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290910-197-defend1827" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290910-197-defend1827" type="age" value="18"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t18290910-197-off1097" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290910-197-off1097" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290910-197-off1097" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290910-197-cd1098" type="crimeDate">19th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-197-off1097 t18290910-197-cd1098"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 3s., the goods of a man unknown, from his person
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290910-197-person1828">
                  GEORGE 
                  SUELTON
               <interp inst="t18290910-197-person1828" type="surname" value="SUELTON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290910-197-person1828" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290910-197-person1828" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a street-keeper. I was on duty at the <placeName id="t18290910-197-crimeloc1099">Seven-dials</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18290910-197-crimeloc1099" type="placeName" value="Seven-dials"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18290910-197-crimeloc1099" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-197-off1097 t18290910-197-crimeloc1099"></join>, on the 19th of July, at a quarter-past eleven o'clock in the morning, and saw the prisoner take this handkerchief from a gentleman's pocket - there was another person just behind him, and as I was following the prisoner the other turned back; I said to him,"Old man, it will not do;" the prisoner then turned back, and I pursued him up Little Andrew-street - as soon as I caught him he took this handkerchief from his hind pocket, and dropped it down; I did lose sight of him, but not for more than half a moment - I had seen him before, and swear he is the man; the gentleman came and said it was his handkerchief - I wanted him to go to the office; he took out his watch, and said he was rather behind time, and would meet me in the evening, but he did not come.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290910-197-person1829">
                  HENRY 
                  HEATHFIELD
               <interp inst="t18290910-197-person1829" type="surname" value="HEATHFIELD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290910-197-person1829" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290910-197-person1829" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was with the witness, and saw the handkerchief taken - he threw it down; the gentleman owned it in the prisoner's presence - the prisoner said he did not take it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I never had it - I was in deep distress, walking along; there was a cry of Stop thief! and I ran - there was a mob round, and this handkerchief laid on the ground.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18290910-197-verdict1100" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290910-197-verdict1100" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 18.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18290910-197-punish1101" type="punishmentDescription">
